divs: Sighting DetailsMy girlfriend and I were heading to dinner and as we walked out the front door this bright star like light caught our eyes in the sky moving towards us.It was flying at 5-10k feet from south [seattle]heading north at 100-200 mph.It flew over us silently as it went north it faded out and I thought it had a little red light at the end but only for 2 secs.I wasnt going to write but I wondered if anyone else saw this so I looked on here and I think I saw the same UFO as this other guy in Seattle so I had to reply.
trends: There have been 30 other sightings in Everett

Summary: Bright like a star but moved like UFO
